<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Singapore Resale Flats Dashboard</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <!-- Start of Self Written Code -->
        <header>
            <h1>Singapore Resale Flats Dashboard</h1>
        </header>

        <!-- Research Questions and Query Buttons -->
        <div>
            <h2>Research Questions</h2>

            <div>
                <p>1. Which town in Singapore has the highest resale price in each month?</p>
                <a href="/resale/town-rankings" class="query-button">
                    <button class="town-rankings">Towns with the Highest Resale Price Every Month</button>
                </a>
            </div>

            <div>
                <p>2. What are the most common types of resale flats?</p>
                <a href="/resale/common-flat-types" class="query-button">
                    <button class="common-flat-types">Most Common Types of Resale Flats</button>
                </a>
            </div>

            <div>
                <p>3. Rank the top 10 years with the most flats built, and what are their average prices?</p>
                <a href="/resale/top10-flats-lease" class="query-button">
                    <button class="top10-flats-lease">Top 10 Years With Most Flats Built</button>
                </a>
            </div>

            <div>
                <p>4. How do the prices vary by flat type across the different towns?</p>
                <a href="/resale/avg-price-type-town" class="query-button">
                    <button class="avg-price-type-town">Average Prices by Flat Type and Town</button>
                </a>
            </div>

            <div>
                <p>5. Are there visible effects of the COVID19 pandemic on the property prices?</p>
                <a href="/resale/effects-of-covid19" class="query-button">
                    <button class="effects-of-covid19">Resale Flat Prices Before COVID19 vs After COVID19</button>
                </a>
            </div>

            <h2>Extra Research Questions to Satisfy the Curious Mind</h2>

            <div>
                <p>6. On which streets were there the Top 10 most resale flats and what are their average resale prices?</p>
                <a href="/resale/most-flats-street" class="query-button">
                    <button class="most-flats-street">Most Number of Flats by Street</button>
                </a>
            </div>

            <div>
                <p>7. What is the average resale price per square meter for every town?</p>
                <a href="/resale/avg-price-sqm" class="query-button">
                    <button class="avg-price-sqm">Average Resale Price per Square Meter</button>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- End of Self Written Code -->
    </div>
    <script src="/js/scripts.js"></script>
</body>

</html>